http://www.getbrickpile.com (no content yet)

#Some BrickPile features
------------------------
RavenDB (both embedded and server)
Easy installation with NuGet
No or very little configuration
Rich UI built in HTML5 and CSS 3
True SEO urls
No required code on the page template (just your own clean markup)
One unified UI for editing all content
HtmlHelpers for creating main and subnavigation with templates for selected page etc
TinyMCE editor for DataType.Html
Custom editor template for creating links between pages
Amazon S3 integration for files
Custom editor template for selecting content images from Amazon S3
RavenDB membership and roleprovider (thanks to Martijn Boland at http://blogs.taiga.nl/martijn/)

